title: Another Place to Write Content
---
body:

I've been using [Trilium](https://github.com/zadam/trilium) to create a personal knowledgebase on my devices. One cool feature is that I choose to make certain groups of notes publicly accessible. Check it out!

Here's the link: https://tril.kevbot.xyz/share/articles

So far the public sections include my recipes, Linux resources, and guides on competitive Super Smash Bros Melee. More to come.

